snippet.title: Robomaze: The Basement gameplay (PC Game, 1991)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Robomaze: The Basement, Dos PC game produced by Wetware in 1991 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/robomaze-the-basement/16998/
Robomaze: The Basement is the third game in the series. It is a very interesting game full of adventure. Worth trying.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
